comments: I learned literary analysis skills, especially on modern prose and poetry.

comments: What I like about this course is that it's discussion oriented. The class size is very comfortable.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes. Whether my friend is an English major or not, the course is really thought provoking and is tightly related to sociology, history, psychology and even mythology.
